<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Magnemite — Verified Campus Hardware Marketplace</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --bg: #080b10;
    --bg-card: #0e1318;
    --bg-glass: rgba(14,19,24,0.85);
    --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    --border-bright: rgba(57,255,120,0.25);
    --green: #39ff78;
    --green-dim: rgba(57,255,120,0.12);
    --green-glow: rgba(57,255,120,0.35);
    --blue: #3de0ff;
    --blue-dim: rgba(61,224,255,0.1);
    --text: #e8edf2;
    --text-muted: #7a8898;
    --text-dim: #4a5566;
    --red-cross: #ff5555;
    --font-head: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    --font-body: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; overflow-x: hidden; }

  body::before {
    content: ''; position: fixed; inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.035'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none; z-index: 999; opacity: 0.4;
  }

  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 18px 6vw; background: rgba(8,11,16,0.75);
    backdrop-filter: blur(18px); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .nav-logo { font-family: var(--font-head); font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.35rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }
  .nav-logo span { color: var(--green); }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a { color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 500; transition: color .2s; }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--green); }
  .nav-cta { background: var(--green); color: #040608; border: none; border-radius: 8px; padding: 9px 20px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; font-family: var(--font-body); transition: box-shadow .2s, transform .15s; }
  .nav-cta:hover { box-shadow: 0 0 22px var(--green-glow); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .hamburger { display: none; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; cursor: pointer; }
  .hamburger span { display: block; width: 22px; height: 2px; background: var(--text); border-radius: 2px; }

  #hero { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 120px 6vw 80px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .hero-grid-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(57,255,120,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(57,255,120,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
    mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 80% at 50% 40%, black 30%, transparent 100%);
  }
  .hero-glow { position: absolute; top: 10%; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 600px; height: 400px; background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(57,255,120,0.10) 0%, transparent 70%); pointer-events: none; }
  .hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 760px; }
  .hero-eyebrow { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: var(--green-dim); border: 1px solid var(--border-bright); border-radius: 100px; padding: 6px 14px; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--green); letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 28px; animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease both; }
  .hero-eyebrow::before { content: '●'; font-size: 0.55rem; animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:.3} }
  .hero h1 { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 4.8rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.06; letter-spacing: -0.03em; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.1s ease both; }
  .hero h1 .accent { color: var(--green); position: relative; display: inline-block; }
  .hero h1 .accent::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -4px; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--green), transparent); border-radius: 2px; }
  .hero-sub { margin-top: 22px; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 540px; line-height: 1.75; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.2s ease both; }
  .hero-sub strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
  .hero-btns { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 14px; margin-top: 42px; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.3s ease both; }
  .btn-primary { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: var(--green); color: #040608; border: none; border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px 28px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; font-family: var(--font-body); transition: box-shadow .2s, transform .15s; text-decoration: none; }
  .btn-primary:hover { box-shadow: 0 0 32px var(--green-glow); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn-secondary { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: transparent; color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border-bright); border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px 28px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; font-family: var(--font-body); transition: background .2s, border-color .2s, transform .15s; text-decoration: none; }
  .btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--green-dim); border-color: var(--green); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .hero-stats { display: flex; gap: 40px; margin-top: 64px; flex-wrap: wrap; animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.4s ease both; }
  .hero-stat-num { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.9rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--green); line-height: 1; }
  .hero-stat-label { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 4px; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(24px) } to { opacity:1; transform:none } }

  section { padding: 100px 6vw; }
  .section-tag { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--green); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .section-h2 { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.025em; line-height: 1.15; }
  .section-sub { color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 14px; max-width: 520px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.75; }
  .section-header { margin-bottom: 64px; }

  .audience-label { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--text-dim); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .audience-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
  .audience-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px 36px; cursor: pointer; transition: transform .22s, border-color .22s, box-shadow .22s; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .audience-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; opacity: 0; transition: opacity .25s; }
  .audience-card:first-child::before { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(57,255,120,0.07) 0%, transparent 60%); }
  .audience-card:last-child::before  { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(61,224,255,0.07) 0%, transparent 60%); }
  .audience-card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); }
  .audience-card:first-child:hover { border-color: rgba(57,255,120,0.35); box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.35); }
  .audience-card:last-child:hover  { border-color: rgba(61,224,255,0.35); box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.35); }
  .audience-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
  .audience-icon-wrap { width: 58px; height: 58px; border-radius: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.7rem; margin-bottom: 20px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .student-icon { background: rgba(57,255,120,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(57,255,120,0.25); }
  .company-icon { background: rgba(61,224,255,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(61,224,255,0.25); }
  .audience-tag { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .audience-card:first-child .audience-tag { color: var(--green); }
  .audience-card:last-child  .audience-tag { color: var(--blue); }
  .audience-title { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.55rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 14px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .audience-body { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.72; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 22px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .audience-body strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
  .audience-perks { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 30px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .audience-perks li { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 300; }
  .audience-cta { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 22px; font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 700; position: relative; z-index: 1; transition: box-shadow .2s; }
  .student-cta { background: var(--green); color: #040608; }
  .company-cta { background: rgba(61,224,255,0.12); color: var(--blue); border: 1px solid rgba(61,224,255,0.3); }

  #how { background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg) 0%, #090d12 100%); }
  .steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 2px; position: relative; }
  .steps::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 52px; left: calc(16.66% + 20px); right: calc(16.66% + 20px); height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border-bright), var(--border-bright), transparent); }
  .step-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 40px 32px; transition: border-color .25s, transform .2s; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .step-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-dim) 0%, transparent 60%); opacity: 0; transition: opacity .25s; }
  .step-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-bright); transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .step-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
  .step-num { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--green); letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .step-icon { width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 12px; background: var(--green-dim); border: 1px solid var(--border-bright); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .step-title { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .step-body { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300; }
  .step-body strong { color: var(--green); font-weight: 500; }

  #marketplace { background: #090d12; }
  .product-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(230px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
  .product-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; transition: border-color .25s, transform .2s, box-shadow .25s; cursor: pointer; }
  .product-card:hover { border-color: rgba(57,255,120,0.3); transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.4); }
  .product-img { height: 160px; background: #0d1520; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 3.2rem; position: relative; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .badge-verified { position: absolute; top: 12px; left: 12px; background: rgba(57,255,120,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(57,255,120,0.4); color: var(--green); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.06em; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 100px; text-transform: uppercase; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; }
  .badge-verified::before { content: '✓'; font-size: 0.7rem; }
  .badge-condition { position: absolute; top: 12px; right: 12px; background: rgba(61,224,255,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(61,224,255,0.25); color: var(--blue); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.6rem; padding: 4px 9px; border-radius: 100px; }
  .product-body { padding: 20px; }
  .product-name { font-family: var(--font-head); font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.98rem; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .product-spec { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 14px; font-family: var(--font-mono); }
  .product-price { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .price-now { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--green); }
  .price-old { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-dim); text-decoration: line-through; text-decoration-color: #ff5555; }
  .price-save { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; color: #ff9f43; background: rgba(255,159,67,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255,159,67,0.2); padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 6px; margin-left: auto; }
  .btn-add { width: 100%; background: var(--green-dim); border: 1px solid var(--border-bright); color: var(--green); border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; font-family: var(--font-body); transition: background .2s, box-shadow .2s; }
  .btn-add:hover { background: rgba(57,255,120,0.2); box-shadow: 0 0 16px var(--green-glow); }
  .marketplace-footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 48px; }
  .marketplace-footer p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }

  #trust { padding: 60px 6vw; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .trust-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 32px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .trust-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .trust-icon { width: 42px; height: 42px; border-radius: 10px; background: var(--green-dim); border: 1px solid var(--border-bright); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .trust-text { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .trust-text strong { display: block; color: var(--text); font-size: 0.92rem; margin-bottom: 2px; }

  #impact { background: var(--bg); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  #impact::before { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -100px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 700px; height: 350px; background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(57,255,120,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%); pointer-events: none; }
  .impact-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: center; }
  .ewaste-box { margin-top: 32px; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-left: 3px solid var(--green); border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px 28px; }
  .ewaste-box h4 { font-family: var(--font-head); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .ewaste-box p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.88rem; line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300; }
  .ewaste-flow { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-top: 16px; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-dim); flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .flow-tag { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px; padding: 5px 10px; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .flow-arrow { color: var(--green); }
  .counters { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); gap: 16px; }
  .counter-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 28px 24px; transition: border-color .25s; }
  .counter-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-bright); }
  .counter-num { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--green); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .counter-label { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.82rem; line-height: 1.4; }
  .counter-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 14px; }

  footer { padding: 64px 6vw 40px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .footer-top { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; margin-bottom: 60px; }
  .footer-brand p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.88rem; margin-top: 14px; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 280px; font-weight: 300; }
  .footer-socials { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-top: 22px; }
  .social-btn { width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; cursor: pointer; transition: border-color .2s, color .2s; text-decoration: none; }
  .social-btn:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); }
  .footer-col h5 { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .footer-col ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 11px; }
  .footer-col ul a { color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; transition: color .2s; font-weight: 300; }
  .footer-col ul a:hover { color: var(--green); }
  .footer-bottom { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 28px; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .footer-bottom p { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.8rem; }
  .footer-bottom .mono { font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--green); font-size: 0.72rem; }

  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 5px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--bg); }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #1e2a36; border-radius: 10px; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    .steps::before { display: none; }
    .impact-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .footer-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .audience-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    nav { padding: 16px 5vw; }
    .nav-links, .nav-cta { display: none; }
    .hamburger { display: flex; }
    section { padding: 72px 5vw; }
    .footer-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
    .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .trust-inner { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 22px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">Mag<span>nemite</span></a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#how">How It Works</a></li>
    <li><a href="#marketplace">Marketplace</a></li>
    <li><a href="#impact">Impact</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
  <button class="nav-cta">Trade In Now →</button>
  <div class="hamburger" id="ham"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
</nav>

<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-grid-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Chandigarh Campus Network · Now Live</div>
    <h1>Don't let your old projects <span class="accent">gather dust.</span> Trade them. Build more.</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      Magnemite is the <strong>campus re-commerce marketplace</strong> for engineering students.
      Turn last semester's Arduino pile into instant cash. Buy verified, working parts
      at <strong>up to 60% off</strong> retail — tested by engineers, for engineers.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#marketplace" class="btn-primary">⚡ Shop Verified Parts</a>
      <a href="#how" class="btn-secondary">↩ Trade-In Your Hardware</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="hero-stat-item">
        <div class="hero-stat-num" data-target="2400">0</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label">Components Tested</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat-item">
        <div class="hero-stat-num" data-prefix="₹" data-target="86000">0</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label">Saved by Students</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat-item">
        <div class="hero-stat-num" data-target="7" data-suffix=" Colleges">0</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label">Campus Nodes Active</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="get-started" style="padding: 0 6vw 90px;">
  <div class="audience-label">I am a —</div>
  <div class="audience-grid">
    <div class="audience-card" onclick="document.getElementById('how').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">
      <div class="audience-icon-wrap student-icon">🎓</div>
      <div class="audience-tag">For Students</div>
      <h3 class="audience-title">College Student</h3>
      <p class="audience-body">Got old Arduinos, dead sensors, or leftover semester project parts piling up? Trade them in for <strong>instant cash payment</strong> and buy verified components at up to 60% off for your next build.</p>
      <ul class="audience-perks">
        <li>✓ Instant cash payout on drop-off</li>
        <li>✓ 340+ verified parts in stock</li>
        <li>✓ 7-day performance guarantee</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="audience-cta student-cta">Sell My E-Waste &amp; Get Paid →</div>
    </div>
    <div class="audience-card" onclick="document.getElementById('contact').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">
      <div class="audience-icon-wrap company-icon">🏭</div>
